      "ariaLabel": "",
      "heading": "AirTrain is the best way to navigate JFK",
      "textPreview": "Reach any on-airport destination in under 20 minutesAirTrain is the best way to navigate JFKWhether you're moving between terminals, leaving the airport via pick-up areas, or headed to public transit, rental cars, or a hotel shuttle, the AirTrain is the easiest way to get around ",
