      "tag": "section",
      "id": "",
      "className": "chakra-stack css-sekf8j",
      "ariaLabel": "",
      "heading": "",
      "textPreview": "You can access public transportation by taking the AirTrain to Jamaica or Howard Beach Station. The one-way AirTrain fare between JFK and these stations is $8.75. To learn more, visit our public transportation page.",
