      "className": "chakra-stack css-sekf8j",
      "ariaLabel": "",
      "heading": "",
      "textPreview": "Heading to your hotel? JFK offers a designated hotel shuttle pickup and dropoff area. Take the AirTrain to Federal Circle via the Jamaica or Howard Beach AirTrain lines to access hotel shuttles.",
